Subject: 2014's Con Chair Roast
Description: Our fearless leader has finally found something to fear - a roasting by his friends and underlings! It's probably all in good fun, but don't expect everyone to be sober.  Speakers include:Nuri Gocay, Dawn Kuczwara, James Gamble, Britain Woodman, Rathbone the Pirate - Track: Penguicon Events  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
